<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/about.css">
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <div class="h">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <div class="btn">
                <a href="http://localhost:3000/home">Home</a>
                <a href="http://localhost:3000/events">Events</a>
                <a href="http://localhost:3000/Registration/event">Registration</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section class="hero-section">
            <h2>Connecting Communities Through Events</h2>
            <p>
                Welcome to our event platform. We specialize in bringing people together for meaningful, 
                educational, and engaging experiences. Whether you are a student, a professional, or an organizer, 
                we make registration and event discovery seamless and straightforward.
            </p>
        </section>

        <div class="grid-section">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>
                    Our mission is to simplify event coordination and attendance. We believe that discovering 
                    transformative seminars, workshops, and gatherings should only be a click away.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Our Vision</h3>
                <p>
                    We envision a connected community where people can easily upgrade their skills, network with industry 
                    leaders, and host impact-driven events effortlessly.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="stats-section">
            <h3>Our Impact</h3>
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-num">10k+</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Active Events</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-num">30k+</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Registrations</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-num">99%</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Satisfaction</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Event Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>